article.description: — Javaunte Hawkins had 20 points in Florida International's 82-74 victory over Maine on Thursday night.
article.headline: Hawkins scores 20, Florida International defeats Maine 82-74
article.linkText: Hawkins scores 20, Florida International defeats Maine 82-74
article.story: MIAMI -- — Javaunte Hawkins had 20 points in Florida International's 82-74 victory over Maine on Thursday night. Hawkins added five rebounds for the Panthers (5-9). Arturo Dean scored 14 points while finishing 6 of 11 from the floor, and added six rebounds and three steals. George Pridgett had 12 points and shot 4 for 8, including 3 for 7 from beyond the arc. Peter Filipovity led the Black Bears (8-6) in scoring, finishing with 16 points, seven rebounds and two steals. Maine also got 13 points from AJ Lopez. Ja'Shonte Wright-McLeish also had 13 points and five steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
